Use the standard library

This is how to compare of game and guess:
   Remember that result is []
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this 6 times:
      Add result to abs of (diff of (item i in game) and (item i in guess))
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is result
Now you know

>>> compare of [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 1] and [1, 2, 3, 4, 2, -2]
[0, 0, 0, 0, 3, 3]
>>> compare of [0, 5, 0, 0, 0, 4] and [4, 1, 1, 0, 0, -2]
[4, 4, 1, 0, 0, 6]
>>> compare of [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 1] and [1, 2, 3, 4, 2, -2]
[0, 0, 0, 0, 3, 3]